flowRoot.flowPara: With enough computational Power you could create avatars (Speech Synthesis / deep fakes) that are "touring complete". I use this word for an avatar that can do everything the real person could also do. And with sociology design patterns and multiple touring complete Avatars you even could simulate complete real-live situations.

So you can never be sure if the person you hear on eg Stimoceiver or US4877027 is really the person or this group you are thinking you talking with. So best thing is to meet face to face (then they abuse this technology too) but if you know this person well you would possibly find out.
